    "patch_code": "private void removeUnrefencedfunctionargs(notationsetter) {\n  if !( notificationsetter.isGet or notificationsetter.isSet ) {return}\n  var in function = notificationsetter.parentNode\n  var in root = function.getroot()\n  var in allvars = root.getvars()\n  var in unrefencedvars = allvars.subSet(notificationsetter.getvars())\n  \n  var in unrefencedarglist = notificationsetter.getparent()\n  var in unrefencedargs = unrefencedarglist.get children()\n  var in unrefencedargs.subSet(notificationsetter.getvars())\n  var in unrefencedvars.add(unrefencedvars)\n  \n  if !( unrefencedvars.isEmpty() ) {return}\n  unrefencedarglist. removechild(notificationsetter)\n}",
